about.summary: A pure-Python implementation of the HTTP/2 priority tree

name: priority
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.3.0" %}

package:
  name: priority
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/p/priority/priority-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6bc1961a6d7fcacbfc337769f1a382c8e746566aaa365e78047abe9f66b2ffbe

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - priority

about:
  home: http://python-hyper.org/priority/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A pure-Python implementation of the HTTP/2 priority tree

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
